      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is in poor condition and will require significant attention from its next owner. The exterior shows heavy wear, including deep scratches, several large dents, and noticeable rust patches on the body panels. Inside, the upholstery is torn in multiple places and the electronics are inconsistent. Mechanically, the engine runs but requires immediate service for a persistent oil leak and suspension issues. This is a project car best suited for someone with the tools and time to restore it.",
