    {
      "id": "detailed_2_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "This vehicle is being sold in poor condition and is best suited as a project car or for parts salvage. The engine currently has a significant oil leak and requires a head gasket replacement to be roadworthy, while the transmission exhibits noticeable slipping. Externally, there is extensive rust on the frame and lower body panels, and the interior upholstery is heavily worn with several tears. It will need to be towed from its current location, but it offers a complete set of original components for a dedicated restorer.",
