    {
      "id": "optimistic_5_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_5",
      "description": "Looking for a budget-friendly project or a basic set of wheels to get you from A to B? This car has plenty of stories to tell and is ready for a new owner who isn't afraid of a little DIY! While it shows significant wear and tear both inside and out, it remains a functional option for anyone looking for the absolute lowest entry point into vehicle ownership. It's a diamond in the rough waiting for the right pair of hands to give it some much-needed attention!",
